
1.get first name and last name from user and print your full name ?

str=raw_input("enter the firstname")
enter the firstname sudharsan
str1=raw_input("enter the lastname")
enter the lastname kumaresan
str2=str+str1
print("the fullname is %s"%str2)
the fullname is  sudharsan kumaresan


2.get your full name, age as input from user and print first name and last name , age using string slicing?
 i) 2 raw_input get name  and age 
 ii) print first name and last name and age 

age=input("enter the age")
enter the age 21
str=raw_input("enter the fullname")
enter the fullname sudharsankuamresan
firstname=str[0:10]
print(firstname)
sudharsan
lastname=str[10:19]
print(lastname)
kuamresan
print("the firstname is %s"%firstname)
the firstname is  sudharsan
print("the lastname is %s"%lastname)
the lastname is kuamresan
print("the age is %s"%age)
the age is 21

3.Calculating your birth number in numerology?

