4.Write a Python program to perform sum of three given integers. 
  However, if any of the two values are equal then sum will be zero ?

num1=input("enter the value")
num2=input("enter the value")
num3=input("enter the value")
if(num1==num2 or num2==num3 or num3==num1):print(0)
else:sum=(num1+num2+num3)
print(sum)

enter the value 30
enter the value 20
enter the value 10
60

